    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1865-06-26T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1865-06-26T00:00:00-05:00" n="374" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d374">
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">Mr. Hunter</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr.
                                Bigelow</persName>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 184.]</seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State,</hi>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington,</hi>
                        </placeName>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1865-06-26">
                            <hi rend="italic">June</hi> 26, 1865.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir:</hi> I have to acknowledge the receipt of your
                            despatch of the 13th instant, No. 117, transmitting a copy of your note
                            of the day before to Mr. Drouyn de Lhuys, correcting certain mistakes
                            which had occurred in representing what you had said and written in
                            regard, respectively, to the position of the United States as to the
                            Mexican question and the revocation to the French decree concerning
                            so-called belligerent rights of the insurgents.</p>
                <p>I am happy to inform you that your note is fully approved.</p>
                <p>I am, sir, your obedient servant,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">W. HUNTER,</hi>
                        <hi rend="italic">Acting Secretary.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">John Bigelow</hi>, Esq., <hi rend="italic">&amp;c., &amp;c., &amp;c., Paris.</hi>
                    </p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
